  "remarks": "TAi.047 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Minister of Information under the Taliban regime. Believed to be in the Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Member of Taliban Supreme Council and member of Taliban Cultural Commission as at 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 21 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 18 Jul 2007, 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov 2011)",
